'''Roland Berland''' (born 26 February 1945) is a former French [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]].<ref name="ProCycling">{{cite web |url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/rider.php?id=168484 |title=Roland Berland |accessdate=27 April 2014 |work=ProCyclingStats}}</ref> He won the [[French National Road Race Championships|French national road race title]] in 1972 and 1979.<ref name="CyclingArchives">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=1955 |title=Roland Berland |accessdate=27 April 2014 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref>

